contract transactions, while December futures moved up 109 points to
close at 6,943, with 4 contracts traded.
</P>
<P>
Taiwan International Mercantile Exchange reference levels for
TAIEX Index futures trading were set Monday at 6,802 for March, 6,815
for April, 6,810 for June, 6,830 for September, and 6,834 for
December.
</P>
<P>
