futures based on Taiwan Stock Exchange-listed electronics shares and
financial stocks, were also higher.
</P>
<P>
March TE futures increased 5.9 points to finish at 280.9, with
11,772 contract transactions, while April TE futures rose 5.3 points
to close at 280.3, with 145 contracts traded.
</P>
<P>
June TE futures gained 5.9 points to finish at 282, with 8
contract transactions, while December TE futures increased 3.95
points to close at 283, with only one contract traded.
</P>
<P>
No transactions were reported for other months.
</P>
<P>
March TF futures moved up 52.8 points to finish at 1,135, with
23,650 contract transactions, while April TF futures rose 52.2 points
to close at 1,135.2, with 169 contracts traded.
</P>
<P>
June TF futures increased 51.6 points to finish at 1,137, with 11
contract transactions, while September TF futures gained 29.4 points
to close at 1,115, with only one contract traded.
</P>
<P>
No transactions were recorded for other months.
</P>
