difficult times over the past year, including the impact of SARS and
the acrimonious disputes between the pilots' union and management
over the issue of pay cuts.
</P>
<P>
But conditions have been improving, and after two quarters of
strong earnings, SIA says it has an "excellent chance" of meeting its
full-year profit targets.
