<HEADLINE>
PRICES UP ON TAIPEI STOCK MARKET
</HEADLINE>
<DATELINE>
Taipei,  Mar.  2 (CNA)
(By Ben Wu)
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Share prices opened high and closed even
higher on the Taiwan Stock Exchange (TAIEX) on Tuesday, with the
weighted index, the market's key barometer, moving up 86.83 points to
close at 6,975.26.
</P>
<P>
The bourse opened at 6,964.66 and fluctuated between 6,984.41 and
6,897.36 during trading.
</P>
<P>
