construction stocks moving up the most at 5.6 percent, followed by
foodstuff shares at 4.4 percent, cement stocks at 3.8 percent,
textile issues at 2.6 percent, electrical shares at 1.6 percent,
plastics and chemical stocks at 0.9 percent, and bank and insurance
shares at 0.6 percent.
</P>
