frontline island of Kinmen, smuggling contraband goods or poaching
were repatriated back to mainland China Thursday.
</P>
<P>
Those deported included nine men and seven women, most of whom
are fishermen residing in Xiamen, in the southeastern mainland
province of Fujian, which lies close to Kinmen.
