they will vote for the "pan-blue alliance" ticket of Kuomintang
Chairman Lien Chan and PFP Chairman James Soong, compared to the
Chen-Lu ticket's 31 percent. And 6.6 percent said they support
neither of the tickets.
</P>
<P>
The poll also found that 85.7 percent said they will go to the
polls; 9.1 percent said they will definitely not or probably not go
to the polls; and 5.1 percent said they have yet to decide whether to
cast ballots in the March 20 presidential election.
</P>
