<P>
Yu lauded the high ability of the Cabinet, citing as examples the
improvement of the water quality of Kaohsiung City, which has long
plagued city residents, the establishment of the Taichung
Science-based Industrial Park and the dredging of the Keelung River.
</P>
<P>
Claiming that the previous Kuomintang (KMT) administrations could
"talk big, but could not act on their words, " Yu accused the KMT of
failing to upgrade industry during its rule, which has resulted in
domestic industries flocking out of Taiwan.
</P>
