Capitalization Weighted Index for March moved up 72 points to close
at 7,051, with 35,888 contracts changing hands.
</P>
<P>
TAIEX index futures for April rose 61 points to finish at 7,070,
with 1,904 contract transactions, while June futures rose 47 points
to close at 7,076, with 31 contracts traded.
</P>
<P>
September futures gained 49 points to finish at 7,098, with 5
contract transactions, while December futures moved up 1 point to
close at 7,070, with 10 contracts traded.
</P>
<P>
Taiwan International Mercantile Exchange reference levels for
TAIEX Index futures trading were set Tuesday at 6,979 for March,
7,009 for April, 7,029 for June, 7,049 for September, and 7,069 for
December.
</P>
<P>
