5,948 contract transactions, while April TE futures rose 1.55 points
to close at 285.5, with 840 contracts traded.
</P>
<P>
June TE futures closed even at 286, with 5 contract transactions,
while September TE futures decreased 5.75 points to finish at 285.55,
with 2 contracts traded. No transactions were recorded for December.
</P>
<P>
