15,460 contract transactions, while April TF futures increased 28.2
points to close at 1,121.2, with 939 contracts traded.
</P>
<P>
June TF futures rose 23.6 points to finish at 1,119, with 4
contract transactions, while September TF futures fell 9.6 points to
close at 1,125, with 2 contracts traded. December TF futures
increased 1 point to finish at 1,130, with 2 contract transactions.
