construction stocks moving up the most at 3.1 percent, followed by
bond and insurance stocks at 2.5 percent, cement stocks at 1.4
percent, textile issues at 1.3 percent, footstuff shares at 1.3
percent, pulp and paper issues at 0.8 percent, plastics and chemical
stocks at 0.6 percent, electrical shares at 0.5 percent.
