TAIPEI STOCK INDEX DOWN BY 78.87 POINTS
</HEADLINE>
<DATELINE>
Taipei, March 12 (CNA)
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Taiwan Stock Exchange (TAIEX) lost
ground on Friday, with the weighted index moving down 78.87 points to
close at 6,800.24.
</P>
<P>
Market turnover amounted to NT$146.07 billion (US$4.36 billion).
</P>
<P>
(By Eric Liu)/Li
