the referendum ballots to show the world that democracy is more
powerful than missiles and dictatorship," Chen said.
</P>
<P>
According to Taiwan's Referendum Act, a nationwide referendum
will be considered valid only if more than half of eligible voters
vote in the referendum.
</P>
<P>
