Beijing ambassador because Taiwan set up a representative office in
Dhaka, Chien said that the report is erroneous.
</P>
<P>
According to the Bangladesh government, the ambassador returned
to Dhaka for personal reasons and was not recalled by the
government, he explained.
</P>
<P>
He said that the Taipei representative office in Dhaka has in
fact expanded its functions since its opening this month and has
begun to have contacts with the Bangladesh government and its people.
</P>
<P>
He stressed that all exchanges with the Bangladesh government
have taken place through normal channels.
