<P>
The American Institute in Taiwan (AIT) ,
which represents U.S. interests in Taiwan in the absence of formal
diplomatic ties, announced Monday that it will reduce its
non-immigrant visa processing fee from NT$3,600 to NT$3,400,
effective April 1.
</P>
