given to Soong at Kuomintang Legislator Tseng Yung-chuan's residence
in December 1994 and he said he hopes Soong will return the political
donation.
</P>
<P>
Huang claimed that he also donated NT$2.7 million to Tseng, NT$2
million to Legislator Wu Tun-yi, NT$2 million to Legislator Hung
Yu-chien and NT$600,000 to Legislator Chu Feng-chih, among others.
</P>
<P>
