invalid votes in the forthcoming presidential election staged a
protest between the campaign headquarters of the two candidates in
the race Wednesday in Taipei.
</P>
<P>
The "Millions for Invalid Votes Union" blamed the two candidates
for ignoring the public desire for a fair and just society.
