</P>
<P>
According to a regulation in the legislature, a bill should be
referred to negotiations between the various parties if any of the
political factions in the legislature request such a move, and if
consensus is still elusive after four months of negotiation , a
bill may be put to the vote anyway.
</P>
<P>
