Kuomintang Chairman Lien Chan announced his decision to file a
lawsuit to declare the just-concluded presidential election invalid
at around 8 p.m., Taipei Mayor Ma Ying-jeou also immediately went to
the Taipei City Police Headquarters to oversee security operations.
</P>
