According to an announcement made by the Central Election
Commission, President Chen Shui-bian and Vice President Annette Lu
won re-election Saturday with 6,471,970 votes in the just-concluded
presidential election, versus 6,442,452 for Lien and his running
mate James Soong.
</P>
