<P>
American Institute in Taiwan
Chairperson Therese Shaheen sent congratulations Friday to President
Chen Shui-bian and Vice President Annette Lu for their re-election,
according to Taiwan's representative office in Washington.
</P>
<P>
Officials of the Taipei Economic and Cultural Representative
Office in the United States said that Shaheen issued his
congratulatory message to Chen and Lu in a telephone call to Chen
Chien-jen, Taiwan's de facto ambassador to U.S. during the absence of
diplomatic ties between the two nations.
