developed into one of the most representative Websites for business
professionals as a result of endeavors to upgrade the content and
Website technology over the last two years and now receives many hits
from foreign traders looking for potential manufacturers. He added
that the Website recorded over 7 million visits last year, which he
said signals an enormous saving in transportation time and cost.
</P>
<P>
Taiwantrade's goal, Lu continued, is to drive forward Taiwan's
global competitiveness. With its popularity growing, world renowned
Websites such as e-Bay and Yahoo Japan have approached Taiwantrade,
Lu said, which will help make Taiwan manufacturers and their products
gain a significant global market share.
