a foreign media outlet on the presidential poll, in which Chen beat
the sole opposition challenger -- Kuomintang Chairman Lien Chan -- by
a razor-thin margin of 0.22 percent, or fewer than 30,000 votes out
of more than 13 million ballots cast.
