possible terror attack.

Hundreds of police in dawn raids seized half a tonne of explosive
material and arrested eight men across London and south-east England
yesterday, in Britain's largest anti-terror operation for years.

The Lianhe Zaobao: Doctors able to access medical data base
online from April 1.

The Health Ministry of Singapore has moved to reassure
Singaporeans that their privacy will be protected when
doctors gain access to a new nationwide medical data base.
The new network will be launched from April 1.
